{"word":"G4422 - πτοέω - ptoéō - pto-eh'-o - Frighten","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πτοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ptoéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pto-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Frighten</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to terrify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a> (through the idea of causing to <i>fall</i>) or to <a href=\"#/G4072 - πέτομαι - pétomai - pet'-om-ahee/4072\">G4072</a> (through that of causing to <i>fly</i> away); to <i>scare:</i> - frighten.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}